    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The engine retains its characteristic 8,000 RPM redline with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed: the rod bearings have been replaced, the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled for timing precision, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The chassis remains tight, utilizing a limited-slip differential and factory-tuned MacPherson strut front/multi-link rear suspension. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with an enthusiast-driven vehicle, the mechanical vitals are excellent, with strong compression and a smooth power band.",
