    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple leather upholstery with light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, while all dashboard electronics, ambient lighting, and dual-zone climate controls function perfectly. Mechanically, it is robust; I have followed a strict synthetic oil change regimen every 5,000 miles, and the brake pads and rotors were replaced just last season. The tires currently show approximately 70% tread life remaining on the original alloy wheels. It starts reliably in all weather conditions and shifts smoothly through all gears. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a folder of service receipts. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
